        <div class="recommendation-item">
          <h2>Ocean to Table</h2>
          <p>What sets Mariscos Jomar apart is their dedication to freshness. All seafood is sourced directly from local fishermen who practice sustainable fishing methods along Costa Rica's Pacific coast. Their offerings change with the seasons and available catch, ensuring you always get the best of what the ocean has to offer.</p>
          
          <p>From delicate white fish like sea bass and snapper to succulent shellfish and shrimp, Mariscos Jomar provides seafood of exceptional quality. Each product is carefully handled and stored to preserve its natural flavor and texture, allowing you to experience the true taste of Costa Rica's coastal waters.</p>
          
