          <p>Their passion for local seafood extends to sustainable practices, supporting fishing methods that help maintain healthy marine ecosystems. By choosing Mariscos Jomar, you're not only treating yourself to exceptional seafood but also supporting responsible fishing in Costa Rica's waters.</p>
          
          <h2>Visit Mariscos Jomar</h2>
          <p>You can find Mariscos Jomar at their stand in Uvita Mercado, where they display their fresh catch daily. For the best selection, visit early in the day when their offerings are at their freshest and most abundant.</p>
